text: Maryam Achak (; born 4 February 1947) is an Iranian fencer. She competed in the women's team foil event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian female fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Iran Category:Fencers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Asian Games gold medalists for Iran Category:Asian Games medalists in fencing Category:Fencers at the 1974 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 1974 Asian Games
